name: Vampire Count
text:
2 Level 6 Monsters
You can also Xyz Summon this card using 1 Level 5 or higher "Vampire" monster as a material. While this card has Xyz material your opponent cannot target "Vampire" cards you control with card effects. You can detach 1 Xyz material from this card and target 1 monster in either player's GY; Special Summon it with its effects negated and if you do it becomes a Zombie monster. You can only Summon 1 "Vampire Count" per turn.
